text.section:
"Licensed other tobacco products manufacturer" means a person licensed by the Comptroller under § 16.5-204(a) of this title who:
manufactures or otherwise produces other tobacco products in the State intended for sale in the State, including other tobacco products intended for sale in the State through an importer; and
sells other tobacco products on which the tobacco tax has not been paid to a licensed other tobacco products wholesaler in the State;
sells other tobacco products on which the tobacco tax has not been paid and which may lawfully be sold in the State to a licensed other tobacco products wholesaler located outside of the State;
unless otherwise prohibited or restricted under local law, this article, or the Criminal Law Article, distributes sample other tobacco products to consumers located in the State; or
stores other tobacco products in an other tobacco products warehouse in the State for subsequent shipment to licensed wholesalers, federal reservations, or persons outside of the State.

"Other tobacco products manufacturer" means a person who:
manufactures or otherwise produces other tobacco products intended for sale in this State, including other tobacco products intended for sale in the United States through an importer;
sells other tobacco products on which the tobacco tax has not been paid to a licensed other tobacco products wholesaler in Maryland;
sells other tobacco products on which the tobacco tax has not been paid and which may lawfully be sold in Maryland to a licensed other tobacco products wholesaler located outside Maryland;
unless otherwise prohibited or restricted under local law, this article, or the Criminal Law Article, distributes sample other tobacco products to consumers located in Maryland; or
stores other tobacco products in an other tobacco products storage warehouse in Maryland for subsequent shipment to licensed other tobacco products wholesalers, federal reservations, or persons out of state; or
is a licensed other tobacco products manufacturer under this title.
